{"tid":1510583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌！台灣驚見藍絲廢老！","createTime":"2019-08-27T08:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T19:02:48.000Z","uid":311962,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"01d82730206168058bbe378ec996966f7c7c5b63","tid":1510583,"uid":311962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"先說在前頭，我是台灣人（請原諒我唔識講廣東話），深黃，從頭到尾參加過台灣太陽花學運<br />\n上次雨傘革命也有關注香港訊息，這次反送中更是每天划手機看連登、香港蘋果、立場新聞<br />\n前幾天終於辦了連登帳號，拒當CDROM（用台大Email申請，Admin還要求學生證照片！）<br />\n<br />\n以下正文：<br />\n週日晚上在台北吃生魚片壽司，整家店只有9個位子，我等深黃巴絲5人，<br />\n店裡還有一對老夫婦、一對年輕人，應該是女兒帶男友來跟爸媽吃飯<br />\n吃到一半，爸爸開始高談闊論香港時事：<br />\n1. 年輕人沒本事、活不下去只會上街搞事<br />\n2. 做錯事要敢做敢當而不是怕被送到中國<br />\n3. 香港水電、做生意都靠中國，根本離不開中國<br />\n幹你娘！聽到差點吃不下去，趕緊回家上連登透氣<br />\n推測這廢老大概也是挺韓國瑜<br />\n年輕人似乎不同意廢老所言，但礙於對方是長輩，不敢造次<br />\n可見即使是台灣，對於香港情勢仍然分兩派<br />\n台灣的情況也跟香港差不多，很多老害挺藍，年輕人親綠居多<br />\n以上報告"},{"pid":"f67678d4376649f3db3de7489251f470d3f7bebf","tid":1510583,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1325aff3a262325be5234ef41aef9d981676441","tid":1510583,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:47:33.000Z","msg":"［開飯/住宿/義診/搵工］你班前線死廢青 未成年中學雞同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果因為發夢需要任何方面嘅協助<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括：需要開飯 / 跟唔到學習進度 / 同屋企人嘈交無零用錢 / 買Gear用曬啲錢 / 同屋企人嘈到要搵宿位/ 發夢受咗傷無錢睇醫生</span><br />\n （所有人都可以申請）</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1949722306331343d2e0d7bbac3f1760497a96da","tid":1510583,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左今天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8c4a5623ae91f3553c48234c2b31a4e5c74b22f","tid":1510583,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=016382e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=6863d74b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=9f633a8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"570f5b75ac1545fffec6d14713a1bdaa1d30f17f","tid":1510583,"uid":311962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"幹，點解bot洗版"},{"pid":"4b37b6f1e741a1f23e237631f82437f5e4baa430","tid":1510583,"uid":89584,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"藍色是智障的顏色 無分國界"},{"pid":"006037caa22f2289e