plyTime":"2019-08-27T09:06:35.000Z","msg":"我看過些街訪，看到有同時支持反送中和韓國魚的人，很搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace1080197d9b37c822c3b32e29f3ce707b49a6e","tid":1510583,"uid":188132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"港台一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我愛台灣"},{"pid":"bf47bd26d2275145af12b080ffb16783dbb66f14","tid":1510583,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"港台聯合戰線"},{"pid":"f1d2a5a4dee1b16cc2ab9f1dba1fec01397544af","tid":1510583,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"香港友人這陣子來台灣幾次，搭車、吃飯遇到朋友總是都會被問說：「香港現在怎麼樣了？」<br />\n香港友人總是微笑說：「你們2020投票投國民黨就知道了。」"},{"pid":"9767f7f343ea816ddcbdc2da091b013719d583fe","tid":1510583,"uid":261018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"謝謝你<br />\n<br />\n我在台灣的朋友也十分支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好感動<br />\n<br />\nps 我朋友也是台大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f96b0254ad4042419ab63f4e556ae757b203e9e","tid":1510583,"uid":311962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9767f7f343ea816ddcbdc2da091b013719d583fe","tid":1510583,"uid":261018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"謝謝你<br />\n<br />\n我在台灣的朋友也十分支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好感動<br />\n<br />\nps 我朋友也是台大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"台大=反共反威權大本營<br />\n幾十年來如一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b03f89462de3c4535ec3542c3eb35dad45c665","tid":1510583,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:40:45.000Z","msg":"有很多人說香港水電來自大陸，其實只是部分正確<br />\n1.電<br />\n香港有超過8成電力係由本地發電<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vu1Vuo4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVu1Vuo4.png&h=dd8bc358&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n只有核能和抽水蓄能電力由廣東提供（只佔16%)<br />\n資料來源：香港環境局<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/tc/about_us/policy_responsibilities/energy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fpolicy_responsibilities%2Fenergy.html&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=497111d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.enb.gov.hk/tc/about_us/policy_responsibilities/energy.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2.水<br />\n的確，香港大部份淡水源自大陸東江水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ompjV6c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FompjV6c.png&h=9ac19a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留意17/18年度集水量，超過7成由廣東東江水輸入（663.58），其餘由香港本地水塘供應<br />\n<br />\n但因為大陸人口增長，廣東水資源開始緊張，所以香港在今年2019年開始興建將軍澳海水化淡廠，預計2022年落成，最多可提供10%用水量，即興建7座化淡廠可完全取代東江水，至於成本問題，海水化淡一開始成本的確偏高，但會逐年下降，最終甚至會便宜過東江水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCcNkz5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCcNkz5.png&h=56457b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源 ：香港水務署<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/publications-and-statistics/pr-publications/the-facts/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublications-and-statistics%2Fpr-publications%2Fthe-facts%2Findex.html&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=8bbc1cc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/publications-and-statistics/pr-publications/the-facts/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/total-water-management-strategy/desalination/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcore-businesses%2Ftotal-water-management-strategy%2Fdesalination%2Findex.html&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=7ccd3f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/total-water-management-strategy/desalination/index.html</a>"}]}